    Introduction to ggswim

    Patient Dataset

    patient_data.Rd

    This dataset provides information about patients, their status, adverse events, and medication administration.

    Usage

    data(patient_data)

patient_status

adverse_events

medication_administration

    Format

    A list containing three tibbles:

    patient_status

    A tibble containing information about patient status including subject ID, cohort, status, name, value, and time sorting.

    adverse_events

    A tibble containing information about adverse events including subject ID, adverse event name, and time of event.

    medication_administration

    A tibble containing information about medication administration including subject ID, medication name, name, and time of event.

    An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 30 rows and 6 columns.

    An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 14 rows and 3 columns.

    An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 8 rows and 4 columns.

    Source

    This dataset is for demonstration purposes only.
